title: Sidewall
description: Vertical rectangle, a full width, giving nearly two repeats. Framework of rocks, shrubs and trees enclosing scenic vignettes; one, a countryside with village, two ruin-crowned hills in background; the other, a river with boats, houses and belfries on bank. Printed in right border: "Allen-Higgins W.P. Co., 2752 "Vogue papers".
